{
  "stem": "3928.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because you could not buy anything, any food, because there was no food.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the money was worthless.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So my aunt, many times, went out to the outlying areas and gave all her jewelry, her rings, you name it, everything, in order to get food, in order to feed all these people.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "By this time, there were at least, in my estimation, 60 people still left in that, you know, in the place.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now feed 60 people just one meal a day, that's not easy, you know, to keep them alive.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And by the way, the people, every day, the men, every day, shaved in that place.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Every day, we-- I told them to shave in case, if anything happened, somebody-- something happen, they have to go on the street.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I don't want them to see them, you know, with beards and everything, to look like they are everyday people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So they did shave, every day, the people under candle light or one little bulb, which was-- you seen it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They were in there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And that's what they did, you know, the people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There were two pregnant women in the place, also.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You know, how they became pregnant, that's not of my business.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] But they, nevertheless, they were-- when they came out, they was-- one of them, a couple of months later, had a baby, you know.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And my aunt and my cousin took care of all these people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Her husband was nowhere to be seen, because he was-- he was just afraid of everything, you know, what-- what happened there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I worked with a man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I know he was a Swede.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I never ask his name, because [LAUGHS] I-- it wasn't my business to asking anybody's name.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
